{"tid":2055894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港大紀元網站開始收費籲支持","createTime":"2020-06-08T10:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T11:27:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d90714745bca71f96e006978ae09921385e150","tid":2055894,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/06/9d9fb782d1ce787281fdd373491f0d34-600x400-600x340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F9d9fb782d1ce787281fdd373491f0d34-600x400-600x340.jpg&h=0873aa41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n創刊19年來，香港大紀元和港人一起，經歷了九七後幾乎所有大風大浪。23條立法，Sars疫情，雨傘革命和反送中運動，大紀元從未缺席。<br />\n<br />\n在辦報初期，我們的大陸記者被拘捕及判刑；在反送中期間，我們的印刷廠被縱火；報紙被便利店下架，中共更加拋出境外勢力言論一直想邊緣化我們，我們的成本沒有辦法平衡。<br />\n<br />\n面對中共，我們從未退縮。在強權和民眾之間，我們支持民眾；在高牆和雞蛋對決中，我們始終選擇反抗高牆，傳播真相、感召良知。<br />\n<br />\n每座城市，都像一個生命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/06/08/a102865872.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F06%2F08%2Fa102865872.html&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=d13c842d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/06/08/a102865872.html</a>"},{"pid":"0673448c8bb5f8c9b94d86b3ed1d8d58d869e69d","tid":2055894,"uid":21493,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"一直有睇<br />\n<br />\n支持你哋<br />\n<br />\n但點解有台灣大紀元app但係無香港app嘅?"},{"pid":"52644bb6efd6a7a51d5d627cf79b1e463fafa074","tid":2055894,"uid":310700,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"Sorry but<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7uiqtLU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7uiqtLU.gif&h=0539e78a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db942609e0a609215f84d478faac8c67414385e2","tid":2055894,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52644bb6efd6a7a51d5d627cf